des:
Adaprox Home products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Adaprox Home products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our " Adaprox Home" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Adaprox Home account in our " Adaprox Home" app;
(3). You need to have some Adaprox Home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our " Adaprox Home" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Adaprox Home" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Adaprox Home" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Adaprox Home", and you'll be navigated to Adaprox Home login page;
(9). Input your Adaprox Home account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
